дия, Великобритания","lifeSummary":"Sir Christopher Seton of Seton родился около 1278 г. Его родителей звали Sir John de Seton of Skelton, Cumberland и Arminia Lascelles. Он женился на женщине по имени Lady Christina De Brus в 1301 г. в местности Шотландия. У них был по крайней мере 1 сын и 1 дочь. Он умер в 1306 г. в местности сетон, хаддингтоншир, Шотландия в возрасте 29 лет и был похоронен в местности Шотландия."},"sm":{"about 1278–1306":"e tusa o le 1278–1306","1278–1306":"1278–1306","1250–1357":"1250–1357","1275–1349":"1275–1349","1295–Female":"1295–Ua Maliu","1222–1299":"1222–1299","–Female":"Ua Maliu","1349":"1349","Abt 1295":"e tusa o le 1295","1357":"1357","1301":"1301","1278":"1278","1299":"1299","1222":"1222","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","about 1278":"e tusa o le 1278","1250":"1250","1306":"1306","Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Sikotilandi","England":"Egelani","Scotland":"Sikotilandi","Seton, East Lothian, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Sikotilandi, United Kingdom"},"sk":{"about 1278–1306":"okolo 1278–1306","1278–1306":"1278–1306","1250–1357":"1250–1357","1275–1349":"1275–1349","1295–Female":"1295–Zosnulá","1222–1299":"1222–1299","–Female":"Zosnulá","1349":"1349","Abt 1295":"okolo 1295","1357":"1357","1301":"1301","1278":"1278","1299":"1299","1222":"1222","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","about 1278":"okolo 1278","1250":"1250","1306":"1306","Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland","England":"England","Scotland":"Scotland","Seton, East Lothian, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Škótsko, Spojené kráľovstvo"},"es":{"about 1278–1306":"aproximadamente 1278–1306","1278–1306":"1278–1306","1250–1357":"1250–1357","1275–1349":"1275–1349","1295–Female":"1295–Fallecida","1222–1299":"1222–1299","–Female":"Fallecida","1349":"1349","Abt 1295":"aproximadamente 1295","1357":"1357","1301":"1301","1278":"1278","1299":"1299","1222":"1222","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","about 1278":"aproximadamente 1278","1250":"1250","130